  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK605">
<l>neṭunīr maṟavi maṭituyi ṉāṉkuṅ </l>
<l>keṭunīrār kāmak kalaṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Procrastination, forgetfulness, idleness, and sleep, these four things, form the vessel which is desired by those destined to destruction.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
